"chatting better](https://delta.chat/en/2017-05-31-delta-makes-chatting-"
"better)."
msgstr ""
"Podeu trobar més motius i raons a l'escrit del blog [Delta makes chatting "
"better](https://delta.chat/en/2017-05-31-delta-makes-chatting-better)."
